Does gender associate with serology (NS1,IgM,IgG) and with Diagnosis (DF,DHF, DSS)?

  -I found there is a significant association between gender and  NS1 *(Male patient seems to have more HS1 than woman)*
   -I found there is a significant association between gender and DSS
  - No association between Gender and IgM and IgG
  - No association between Gender and DF and DHF

    -Same with IgG
    - No association beetwen age group and DF, DHF
    -With DSS,i found association.It seems that patient with age beetween 18-19, are more unlike to contract DSS
